        {
            "title": "德甲｜穆斯亞拿傷出 拜仁慕尼黑3:1慘勝奧格斯堡",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"穆斯亞拿傷出，拜仁慕尼黑3:1慘勝奧格斯堡。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f04e1c0926685e58e349e2bb93ad4050/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250405/_2025040513421571937.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">穆斯亞拿傷出，拜仁慕尼黑3:1慘勝奧格斯堡。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>拜仁慕尼黑於周五的德甲獨腳戲作客3:1反勝奧格斯堡，但卻要付上沉重代價，陣中的德國中場穆斯亞拿（Jamal Musiala ）下半場傷出。而拜仁下周二便要在歐聯8強首回合主場出戰國際米蘭，前鋒哈利卡尼坦言穆斯亞拿的情況實在令人擔心。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁慕尼黑(紅衫)3:1反勝奧格斯堡(白衫)。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/de14f28609b1c430e79a2305f25cdbb4/2025-04/2025-04-04T185412Z_1677028781_UP1EL441GIBZ2_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁慕尼黑(紅衫)3:1反勝奧格斯堡(白衫)。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利萊辛尼(右)射門逼使對方後衛擺烏龍。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f0fa3ad4c8f44dde082d82e111f92110/2025-04/2025-04-04T203343Z_1791089809_UP1EL441KW94T_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利萊辛尼(右)射門逼使對方後衛擺烏龍。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"中場基安諾里斯(白衫)為奧格斯堡先開紀錄。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1229e07d96a94e1c26d13116b639769a/2025-04/2025-04-04T190355Z_2131927353_UP1EL441GYHZG_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        中場基安諾里斯(白衫)為奧格斯堡先開紀錄。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁中場穆斯亞拿受傷需要工作人員扶離場。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cc96ce3624912242fe2c904c2af89e4/2025-04/2025-04-04T200141Z_672636058_UP1EL441JMR39_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁中場穆斯亞拿受傷需要工作人員扶離場。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁中場穆斯亞拿受傷需要工作人員扶離場。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/93e0b200065fead7f8128e25a88c19dc/2025-04/2025-04-04T195856Z_2000858147_UP1EL441JI735_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁中場穆斯亞拿受傷需要工作人員扶離場。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁前鋒哈利卡尼(右)被對手侵犯。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/38cc0ac46a748cb0406c824ca3b3e1fd/2025-04/2025-04-04T200353Z_1217422527_UP1EL441JQF3D_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁前鋒哈利卡尼(右)被對手侵犯。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁慕尼黑(紅衫)3:1反勝奧格斯堡(白衫)。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5264f0bbff1d5a00fecdf57948044b08/2025-04/2025-04-04T200453Z_1442652651_UP1EL441JS43J_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁慕尼黑(紅衫)3:1反勝奧格斯堡(白衫)。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拜仁慕尼黑教練高柏尼對於穆斯亞拿受傷感到擔心。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa7cb2542bb66a23a9022798c90a10d1/2025-04/2025-04-04T203214Z_528951499_UP1EL441L1P50_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-GERMANY-FCA-FCB-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拜仁慕尼黑教練高柏尼對於穆斯亞拿受傷感到擔心。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>賽前被看淡的奧格斯堡，31分由後衛古維利奧罰球傳入禁區，中場基安諾里斯禁區左邊避過拜仁後衛干拉特賴馬再施射破網，為主隊先開紀錄。作客的拜仁上半場完結前3分鐘，由前鋒利萊辛尼左路底線傳中，中場穆斯亞拿12碼點附近於對方後衛包圍下，轉身抽射入網，助拜仁追和1:1返回更衣至。\n\n</p><h2>薛斯亞領紅奧格斯堡十人應戰</h2>\n<p>換邊後，拜仁52分鐘有反先機會，米高奧利斯接應利萊辛尼左路傳中，門前左腳抽射中楣彈出。拜仁入波不成，更有穆斯亞拿因傷退下火線。戰至58分鐘，奧格斯堡後衛薛斯亞從後鏟跌哈利卡尼接獲第二面黃牌被逐。拜仁馬上把握罰球機會，由哈利卡尼接應米高奧利斯右路傳中，門前頭槌破網反超前2:1。補時階段，利萊辛尼禁區左邊窄位起腳，逼使敵衛馬特森馬擺烏龍，助拜仁奠定3:1勝局。\n\n</p><h2>哈利卡尼擔心穆斯亞拿傷情</h2>\n<p>不過，穆斯亞拿的受傷恐怕影響他在下周二歐聯8強首回合主場對國際米蘭上陣，隊友哈利卡尼亦表示擔心：「今仗在落後之下反勝並不容易，球隊的心態非常好，最重要是拿到3分。穆斯亞拿受傷實令人擔心，希望情況不會太差。面前還有很多重要比賽，我們必須團結共度難關。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
